# keeplist — accounts to never suggest unfollowing.
#
# One username per line (without the leading @). Lines starting with '#' and
# blank lines are ignored. Matching is case-insensitive.
#
# Use this for accounts the heuristics can't be trusted on: brands/public
# figures you deliberately keep, or personal accounts with sparse export
# signal that you know you want to hold onto.
#
# Examples (commented out):
# natgeo
# a_close_friend_with_no_dms
